{"tid":444170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★icable始終係icable！","createTime":"2017-10-22T09:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T12:15:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c4249f306dd7a20b5d5fbd16bce80a0dfdc38359","tid":444170,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有線電視故障　畫面冇嘢睇客戶嬲爆</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171022/photo/bkn-20171022135604411-1022_00822_001_01b.jpg?20171022152050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171022%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171022135604411-1022_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20171022152050&h=879b4095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線電視今日(22日)發生故障，多名讀者向東網表示，今早開始無法收看有線各個頻道，畫面被鎖、無法轉台、畫面不停顯示「系統更新」，亦無法致電有線的客戶服務熱線，「好似死晒機咁」。有線電視回應指，部分用戶今早出現接收問題，經了解情況後已即時作出跟進，現已全面恢復正常播映。<br />\n<br />\n讀者陳先生使用有線電視服務約10年，他今早轉台時，畫面突然被「hold死」，並出現「系統正在更新中」的字句，亦無法轉台。即使重新啟動解碼器，但問題仍然持續。他致電客戶服務熱線，「一打就斷線，好似死晒機咁」，直至下午1時許，才恢復正常，但已錯過想收看的節目。<br />\n<br />\n不過，仍有部分有線電視用戶未能正常收看節目，畫面顯示一片雪花或藍幕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171022/bkn-20171022135604411-1022_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171022%2Fbkn-20171022135604411-1022_00822_001.html&d=QyXU194jRvXZQ7BW7U48ZwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=fb7c54ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171022/bkn-20171022135604411-1022_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0ccd19ab6e17f86b4c6375116c1e9e50b1f1105f","tid":444170,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df07a816c26d845988b6a40fc0d76087e824ed19","ti